                <h1>Mastering Foley: The Art of Sound Design in Film</h1>
                <p>Foley is a crucial aspect of sound design in film and television, involving the reproduction of everyday sound effects that enhance the viewer's experience. By creating live, synchronized sound effects in post-production, Foley artists add realism to scenes, from footsteps to rustling clothes, making the story come alive for audiences.</p>
